&lt;p&gt;My goal is for this article to give someone a jump start on system automation in smaller mixed environments. You are likely a network engineer or sysadmin who has some experience in the field and has heard a lot about Python or Powershell automation. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SaltStack is a wonderful framework to get you automating without having to solve the difficult problems with distributed computing. &lt;/p&gt;
